Create a Repository: Go to GitHub and create a new repository (e.g., restaurant-menu-app).

Clone to VS Code: Open the terminal in VS Code and run:

Bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/restaurant-menu-app.git
cd restaurant-menu-app
Add Files: Move your index.html file into this folder.

Commit and Push:

Bash
git add .
git commit -m "Initial commit: Added HTML menu"
git push origin main
